Package stincmale.ratmex.executor

Class SubmitterWorkerScheduledTaskConfig<E extends RateMeasuredEvent,SRS,WRS>

  • java.lang.Object
    • stincmale.ratmex.executor.ScheduledTaskConfig<E>
      • stincmale.ratmex.executor.SubmitterWorkerScheduledTaskConfig<E,SRS,WRS>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - A type of container with data provided to RateListener by RateMeasuringExecutorService.
    SRS - A type that represents statistics of submitter RateMeter.
    WRS - A type that represents statistics of worker RateMeter.

    @Immutable
public class SubmitterWorkerScheduledTaskConfig<E extends RateMeasuredEvent,SRS,WRS>
extends ScheduledTaskConfig<E>
    A configuration of a scheduled task for SubmitterWorkerRateMeasuringExecutorService.

    The default values:

    • The default values from ScheduledTaskConfig
    • getSubmitterRateMeterSupplier() - Must be explicitly specified, there is no default value
    • getWorkerRateMeterSupplier() - Must be explicitly specified, there is no default value
